<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="id">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Impian Kita - Wedding Planner</title>
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Kalam&family=Playfair+Display:wght@600&family=Poppins:wght@400;600&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/style.css">
  <style>
    /* ===== Navbar ===== */
    nav {
      display: flex;
      justify-content: space-between;
      align-items: center;
      padding: 1rem 8%;
      background-color: #fff;
      box-shadow: 0 2px 6px rgba(0,0,0,0.05);
      position: sticky;
      top: 0;
      z-index: 100;
    }

    .logo {
      font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
      font-size: 1.5rem;
      font-weight: 600;
      color: #991b1b;
      text-decoration: none;
    }

    .nav-links {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 1.5rem;
    }

    .nav-links a {
      text-decoration: none;
      color: #444;
      font-weight: 500;
      transition: color 0.3s;
    }

    .nav-links a:hover {
      color: #991b1b;
    }

    .nav-buttons a {
      background-color: #991b1b;
      color: #fff;
      padding: 0.5rem 1.2rem;
      border-radius: 2rem;
      text-decoration: none;
      font-weight: 600;
      font-size: 0.9rem;
      margin-left: 0.5rem;
      transition: background-color 0.3s ease;
    }

    .nav-buttons a:hover {
      background-color: #b22222;
    }

    /* ===== Hero Section ===== */
    .hero {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: space-between;
      padding: 4rem 8%;
      background-color: #fff;
      min-height: 90vh;
    }

    .hero-text {
      flex: 1;
      max-width: 550px;
    }

    .hero-text h1 {
      font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
      font-size: 2.5rem;
      color: #991b1b;
      margin-bottom: 1rem;
    }

    .hero-text p {
      font-size: 1.1rem;
      color: #444;
      margin-bottom: 2rem;
      line-height: 1.6;
    }

    .hero-text a {
      background-color: #991b1b;
      color: #fff;
      padding: 0.75rem 1.5rem;
      border-radius: 2rem;
      text-decoration: none;
      font-weight: 600;
      transition: background-color 0.3s ease;
    }

    .hero-text a:hover {
      background-color: #b22222;
    }

    .hero-img {
      flex: 1;
      text-align: right;
    }

    .hero-img img {
      width: 90%;
      border-radius: 1rem;
      box-shadow: 0 4px 10px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
    }

    /* ===== Section: About ===== */
    .about {
      padding: 5rem 8%;
      background-color: #f8f9fa;
      text-align: center;
    }

    .about h2 {
      color: #991b1b;
      font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
      margin-bottom: 1rem;
      font-size: 2rem;
    }

    .about p {
      color: #555;
      max-width: 700px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      line-height: 1.7;
      font-size: 1rem;
    }

    /* ===== Section: Footer ===== */
    footer {
      background-color: #991b1b;
      color: #fff;
      text-align: center;
      padding: 1.5rem 0;
      font-size: 0.9rem;
      letter-spacing: 0.3px;
    }

    /* ===== Responsive ===== */
    @media (max-width: 768px) {
      nav {
        flex-direction: column;
        gap: 1rem;
      }

      .hero {
        flex-direction: column;
        text-align: center;
      }

      .hero-img {
        margin-top: 2rem;
      }

      .hero-img img {
        width: 100%;
      }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>

  <!-- Navbar -->
  <%- include('partials/navbar', { user }) %>

  <!-- Hero Section -->
  <section class="hero">
    <div class="hero-text">
      <h1>Wujudkan Pernikahan Impian Kalian</h1>
      <p>“Impian Kita” hadir untuk membantu pasangan mewujudkan hari bahagia dengan perencanaan pernikahan yang elegan, mudah, dan berkesan.</p>
      <a href="/signup">Mulai Sekarang</a>
    </div>

    <div class="hero-img">
      <img src="/hero-img.jpeg" alt="Wedding Illustration">
    </div>
  </section>

</body>
</html>
